fields.label:
HSI16 clock enable.
Set and cleared by software.

HSI16 always enable for peripheral kernels.
Set and cleared by software to force HSI16 ON even in Stop modes.

settings.label: HSI16 oscillator is forced ON even in Stop mode

fields.label:
HSE clock enable.
Set and cleared by software.

HSE crystal oscillator bypass.
Set and cleared by software to bypass the oscillator with an external clock.

settings.label: HSE crystal oscillator bypassed with external clock

fields.label:
Clock security system enable.
Set by software to enable the clock security system.

settings.label: Clock security system OFF (clock detector OFF)
Clock security system ON (Clock detector ON if the HSE oscillator is stable, OFF if not)

fields.label:
Main PLL enable.
Set and cleared by software to enable the main PLL.
HSI16 clock trimming These bits provide an additional user-programmable trimming value that is added to the HSICAL[7:0] bits.

System clock switch.
Set and cleared by software to select system clock source (SYSCLK).

AHB prescaler.
Set and cleared by software to control the division factor of the AHB clock.

APB1 prescaler.
Set and cleared by software to control the division factor of the APB1 clock (PCLK1).

APB2 prescaler.
Set and cleared by software to control the division factor of the APB2 clock (PCLK2).

Microcontroller clock output.
Set and cleared by software.

settings.label: MCO output disabled, no clock on MCO

fields.label:
Microcontroller clock output prescaler.
These bits are set and cleared by software.

Main PLL entry clock source.
Set and cleared by software to select PLL clock source.

settings.label: HSI16 clock selected as PLL clock entry
HSE clock selected as PLL clock entry

fields.label:
Division factor for the main PLL input clock.
Set and cleared by software to divide the PLL input clock before the VCO.

Main PLL multiplication factor for VCO.
Set and cleared by software to control the multiplication factor of the VCO.

Main PLL PLL P clock output enable.
Set and reset by software to enable the PLL P clock output of the PLL.

Main PLL division factor for PLL P clock.
Set and cleared by software to control the frequency of the main PLL output clock PLL P clock.

Main PLL Q clock output enable.
Set and reset by software to enable the PLL Q clock output of the PLL.

Main PLL division factor for PLL Q clock.
Set and cleared by software to control the frequency of the main PLL output clock PLL Q clock.

PLL R clock output enable.
Set and reset by software to enable the PLL R clock output of the PLL (used as system clock).

Main PLL division factor for PLL R clock (system clock).
Set and cleared by software to control the frequency of the main PLL output clock PLLCLK.
Main PLLP division factor Set and cleared by software to control the PLL P frequency.

settings.label: PLL P clock is controlled by the bit PLLP

fields.label:
LSE oscillator enable.
Set and cleared by software.

LSE oscillator bypass.
Set and cleared by software to bypass oscillator in debug mode.

LSE oscillator drive capability.
Set by software to modulate the LSE oscillators drive capability.

settings.label: Xtal mode medium low driving capability
Xtal mode medium high driving capability

fields.label:
CSS on LSE enable.
Set by software to enable the Clock Security System on LSE (32 kHz oscillator).

RTC clock source selection.
Set by software to select the clock source for the RTC.

settings.label: LSE oscillator clock used as RTC clock
LSI oscillator clock used as RTC clock
HSE oscillator clock divided by 32 used as RTC clock

fields.label:
RTC clock enable.
Set and cleared by software.

RTC domain software reset.
Set and cleared by software.

Low speed clock output enable.
Set and cleared by software.

Low speed clock output selection.
Set and cleared by software.

LSI oscillator enable.
Set and cleared by software.

Remove reset flag.
Set by software to clear the reset flags.

HSI48 clock enable.
Set and cleared by software.
